{"tid":1755004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民應該捐人工","createTime":"2019-11-25T11:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T13:03:42.000Z","uid":276188,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb0d77ff7cc1385393d6ca343da82f4b0e7b97b","tid":1755004,"uid":276188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:56:40.000Z","msg":"區選前係咁講區議會有好多資源,宜家選到係咪應該運用泛民得到嘅資源?既然泛民都知佢地贏係因為義士嘅付出,咁就應該幫返啲義士。唔洗好多,每個議員每個月捐一萬,個基金每個月就有大概400萬,區議會+立法會嘅議員就再捐多啲,個基金唔收公眾捐款嘅話就可以做啲612做唔到嘅野（例如Gear）,同埋失業支援,被捕支援,法律支援都唔洗再籌錢,基金管理人由投票決定,收益公開,合法支出公開,敏感支出就可以有保留。大家點睇?"},{"pid":"d9e52d996f6f3c519488fdd6b3bcd8ac5e0f45e1","tid":1755004,"uid":42764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:09:17.000Z","msg":"唔求一萬，十一奉獻都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ad5546b7c7408d07c5140cfb03900c6a31ee0d","tid":1755004,"uid":119767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:14:12.000Z","msg":"我求佢地優先請抗爭者做助理<br />\n等佢地有兩餐溫飽再去反抗已經好好"},{"pid":"c9bf8035cd3fa375ba6d091a00404fd5e8667e43","tid":1755004,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:17:15.000Z","msg":"成立基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5adb24c0ec54044dda68f74eadce882b96edf75f","tid":1755004,"uid":87715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:20:25.000Z","msg":"小麗老母咩"},{"pid":"dda61b5c3ecee83969b7850d5d88c4ba600b2365","tid":1755004,"uid":147664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"白撚痴 你自己唔捐？"},{"pid":"2d26fa6db523b790165712edf1107a2c5a168717","tid":1755004,"uid":276188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dda61b5c3ecee83969b7850d5d88c4ba600b2365","tid":1755004,"uid":147664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"白撚痴 你自己唔捐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:26:39.000Z","msg":"我想問我有邊句話唔捐?我只係叫泛民將佢地因為義士付出而得到嘅資源回饋返義士身上,有咩問題